The paper deals with hybrid analog/digital precoding in millimeter wave MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and communications (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of OFDM, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM), and the use of antenna arrays, which is a topic related to computer architecture (cs.AR).
